    "In 1993, Beck published an account of his legal battles over art restoration, <em>Art Restoration: the Culture, the Business and the Scandal</em>, co-written by his colleague Michael Daley.": [],
    "A lay text, <em>Three Worlds of Michelangelo</em> was issued in 1999.": [],
    "Beck published <em>From Duccio to Raphael: Connoisseurship in Crisis</em>, a book questioning the attribution of Raphael to the Madonna of the Pinks, National Gallery, and of Duccio's attribution to the Stoclet Duccio (\"Duccio Madonna\") to the Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York.": [],
